*.swo
*~
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace

# IDE config dirs MUST be committed — they carry VS Code settings, extensions,
# launch configs, and title-bar colorization that the team shares.
# AI agent config dirs MUST also be committed — they carry skills and instructions.
# DO NOT add .vscode/, .idea/, .claude/, .codex/, .agents/, .cline/, .opencode/,
# .github/copilot-instructions.md, .cursorrules, .windsurfrules, or similar.

